  m_Name: Samurai - World Boss Exorcist - Before Fight
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  data:
    convoName: Samurai - World Boss Exorcist - Before Fight
    lines:
    - character: Akihito
      expression: 
      line: "We don\u2019t really know what we are up against here, do we? "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "You fought him already. Don\u2019t you know exactly what we\u2019re
        up against? "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Akihito
      expression: 
      line: 'That was so soon after his return. He was being brash and irrational.
        His fighting was sloppy, but just the sheer number of yokai he summoned overwhelmed
        me. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'Then I expect we will be fighting many more of them. Were you trained
        to fight those monsters? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Akihito
      expression: 
      line: 'Partially. My training was to improve my swordsmanship and my resolve.
        Both of these assist in any fight. However, the most experience I had fighting
        yokai was from my youth. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "I\u2019m supposed to believe that you killed those things as a child? "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Akihito
      expression: 
      line: "I had to. Most in the family of the Kanazawa Clan had the capability
        of exorcizing and controlling the yokai. When my parents forced me to go
        alone and capture some that had been wandering the streets, I had to adapt.
        If I couldn\u2019t use magic, I would have to rely on my physical abilities. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'Impressive. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Akihito
      expression: 
      line: 'What is your plan, here? Just go in and kill him? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "And if I say it is? It\u2019s the most effective way to halt the incoming
        calamity. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Akihito
      expression: 
      line: 'You would kill someone whose life you ruined just because they were
        rightfully furious?  '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "\u2026 We need to go now."
      audio: {fileID: 0}
